FBIS4-4355 "dreas062_n_94006" FBIS-EAS-94-062 Daily Report 30 Mar 1994 Vietnam Embassy in Germany Denies Aiding Asylum Seekers Embassy in Germany Denies Aiding Asylum Seekers BK3003133294 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 1100 GMT 30 Mar 94 BK3003133294 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network Vietnamese BFN [Text] In recent days, some mass media in the FRG have reported that the Vietnamese Government has supported certain organizations in bringing people from Vietnam to apply illegally for asylum in the FRG, and that the Vietnamese Embassy in the FRG legalized documents for these asylum seekers. The Vietnamese Embassy in the FRG totally denies all of this incorrect information. It confirms that the Vietnamese Government never tolerates such illegal actions. The Vietnamese Embassy in the FRG has resolutely refused to issue any documents to asylum seekers living illegally in the FRG.
